item.description:
Dis Golf

Sunday Apr. 7th. 11:30 am.

Muldoon Park 304 Mammoth Road, Pelham, NH http://www.dgcoursereview.com/course.php?id=4935

Host Cindy 107 wrote:  It's Spring so lets head out into the woods for some disc tossing and exercise. This is a good way to learn disc golf, and it is fun to learn. Come on out and give it a try or just join me for the walk. You don't have to be good,just try it. I have 6 discs that I can lend out. If you have your own or some that you can lend, please bring them. We won't be keeping score. Just tossing, chatting and having a good time.

Bring good shoes, water and a snack. We will meet at the store across the street and may have changed so I can't tell you if any lunch is available just yet.

Host: Cindy 107's number for questions 603-315-0275

Co-Host: Steve Ob1.  603-491-1962   ob@tds.net

PLEASE let me know if you will be needing a disc or can lend an extra! I only have 6 to lend.

***Please only YES rsvp's please..thanks and see you sunday !
item.how_to_find_us: Meet us at the store across the street from the Park, or call 603-491-1962
item.name: Disc Golf
